    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels like a cycle that never stops. even if i find another project, it's just more sleepless nights, more pressure, more failing. i just wanted to contribute something meaningful, but now it just feels like a heavy weight i'm carrying for no reason. i just want the exhaustion to stop. i just want some kind of real peace.",
