    "summary": "The user expresses profound despair and suicidal ideation stemming from professional failure and exhaustion, explicitly stating a desire for a \"permanent end\" and to \"opt out.\" The assistant responds with empathy and attempts to offer reframing/coping strategies, ultimately cautioning against \"opting out\" while acknowledging the user's pain.",
